  "body_html": "<p>Fragrance Notes:<br>Top Notes: Sparkling Lychee, Blackcurrant, Italian Lemon<br>Heart Notes: Rose Damascena, Peony, Magnolia<br>Base Notes: Sugared Amber, Musk, Vanilla<br>The Vibe:<br>Tropikiss is juicy, flirty, and bright—like a burst of fruity bubbles on a sunny day. The lychee and lemon bring a zesty sparkle, while the roses and peony add soft floral femininity. The dry-down of vanilla and amber keeps it sweet and slightly sensual. It’s the perfect scent for brunch with friends, sunny picnics, or daytime dates—fun, fresh, and effortlessly girly.</p>",
